To remove an item from your wishlist, open the wishlist in the app, locate the item you want to delete, tap the three-dot menu or heart icon next to it, and choose “Remove from Wishlist” to immediately remove it.
To subscribe to premium, open the app, go to the Profile or Subscription section, tap Subscribe or Upgrade to Premium, choose your plan, and follow the on-screen payment instructions.
To download movies, open the app, go to the movie you want, tap the Download button (usually a downward arrow), and the movie will be saved to your device for offline viewing.
To unsubscribe from premium, open the app, go to Profile or Subscription settings, tap Manage Subscription or Cancel Premium, and follow the prompts to confirm cancellation.
To add content to your list, open the app, navigate to the movie or show you want, tap the Add to My List or + button, and it will appear in your personal list.
